This paper deals with mobile data transparency and proposes a network-based approach to inspect packets generated by mobile devices. The paper focuses on applying Federated Learning to mobile packet classification, which involves model and feature selection, and tuning the Federated Learning parameters. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category for this paper is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security), followed by cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture), cs.SI (Social and Information Networks), and cs.MM (Multimedia).
